        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Advancing Innovation in Alternative Pain and Addiction Therapies Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Food and Drug Administration to issue guidance clarifying eligibility and&nbsp;criteria for the accelerated approval&nbsp;of non-opioid or nonaddictive drugs to treat pain or substance-use disorders.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
